Package rs.ac.bg.fon.np_project.commonlibrary.model

Class Worker

java.lang.Object
rs.ac.bg.fon.np_project.commonlibrary.model.AbstractDO
rs.ac.bg.fon.np_project.commonlibrary.model.Worker
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class Worker
extends AbstractDO
implements java.io.Serializable
Predstavlja domensku klasu zaposlenog. Sadrzi atribute: id, username, password, firstName, lastName i loggedIn. Ovi atributi su vezani za identifikaciju zaposlenog. Takodje, nalaze se i get i set metode zajedno sa metodama iz klase AbstractDO.
Version:
1.0.0
Author:
Simona
See Also:
